  4. [38;5;10mmap_facts_to_criteria[0m — SATISFIED/PARTIAL/UNMET/CONTRADICTED assessment plus blocking-gap detection[0m[0m
  5. [38;5;10mretrieve_supporting_evidence[0m — clinical evidence KB retrieval with citation metadata, skipping uncited chunks[0m[0m
